Description: ==========================================
        Datepicker (collective.z3cform.datepicker)
        ==========================================
        
        jqueryui datepicker integration for z3cform's and plone. Enjoy ...
        
        source: http://github.com/garbas/collective.z3cform.datepicker
        
        
        TODO
